Upon starting it will prompt to ask if you want to go first or second.
inputing "1" will have you go first where any other input will default to second.

it will then ask which token you would like to be.
inputting "W" or "w" will have you be white where any other input will default to black.

when it is your turn it will ask for which box you will like to place a piece in (1-4)
after that it will ask for which position in that box(1-9) 
if either input is invalid then you will be prompted to enter both again.

when won player wins the program will stop.